quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  17,23,"Joomi maa yamirii :\"Wata on rewu ko wanaa Kanko, jibimЙ“e Й“en,moЖҙЖҙagol [e maЙ“Й“e]:si nayewu goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e yottike ma,maa Й—um Й“e Й—iЙ—o non;wata a wiвҖҷan Й“e \"bis=uf!\" wata a wikko Й“e =wota a furo,wowlan Й“e konngol teddungol"
  17,24,"YankinanoЙ—aa Й“e yurmeЙ—aa Й“e, wiвҖҷaa: В« Joomi an, yurme Й“eвҖҷe, wano Й“e neвҖҷirnoo lan non hari ko mi tosokun В»"
  17,25,"Joomi mo'on no Anndi ko woni ka nder wonkiiji mon, si tawii on wonuno moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e ; pellet Kanko O wonanii ruttotooЙ“e Й“en Surroowo"
  17,26,"Jonnu jom Й“adondiral haqqee makko on, e Й“illiiЙ—o, e seteejo haqqee makko on ; wata a funsu funsudee"
  17,27,"Pellet funsooЙ“e Й“en, ko siЙ—Й“e seytanuuji Й—in ; seytaane non wonii yedduЙ—o Joomi mun"
  17,28,"Si a Й—urnike Й“e fii Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, nde jortiЙ—aa Й—um, wi'an Й“e konngol newiingol"
  17,29,"Wata a waЙ—u junngo maa ngon ko lmbaango, ka daande maa ; wata a fontu ngo kadi kala fontugol, haa jooЙ—oЙ—aa ko a felniiЙ—o, ninsuЙ—o"
  17,30,"Pellet Joomi maa, no yanГұana arsike, on Mo O muuyi. O Й“ittina. Pellet Kanko O wonii HumpitiiЙ—o, YiвҖҷoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko"
  17,31,"Wota on warir Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Й“en kulol Й“illa=baasal, ko Menen arsikata Й“e, wonndude e mon ; pellet warugol Й“e ngol, wonii goopol manngol"
  17,32,"Wota on Й“atto jeeno ngon=fijrde nde, pellet Й—un wonii pankare e laawol bonungol"
  17,33,"Wata on waru wonkii, ki Allah harmini kin [warugol], si wonaa sabu hakkee. Mo tooГұaama waraama, Men waЙ—anii heftuЙ“e e makko Й“en doole wota non o fantin ka warugol. Pellet Kanko o wonii wallaaЙ—o"
  17,34,"Wata on Й“atto jawle Alyatiim, si wonaa Й“attagol Й“urngol moЖҙЖҙude, haa sagatalaaku makko timma ; humnee aadi ndin; pellet, aadi ndin wonii lannditoytee ndi"
  17,35,"Hunnee Й“etu ngun si on etay, manndikiron manndakke=peeson peese feewuЙ—e, ko Й—un moЖҙЖҙi, ko kaГұun Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude battane"
  17,36,"Wata a naatu e ko a anndaa fii mun. Pellet nanЙ—e Й—en, e giiЙ—e Й—en e Й“ernde nden, Й—iiЙ—oo fow wonii lannditoyteeЙ—i ka Makko"
  17,37,"Wata a yaaru ka leydi ГұaaЖҙa bunnga, ko fii pellet an a yulataa leydi ndin, a yottotaako pelle Й—en junndi=njuuteendi"
  17,38,"Й—in fow, bone majji on wonii aГұaaЙ—un ka Joomi maa"
  17,39,"ЖҠun, ko goЙ—Й—un e ko Joomi maaЙ—a wahayini faade e maa, immorde e Г‘eeГұal wata a waЙ—u reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla, sakko werleЙ—aa ka nder jahannama ko a felaaЙ—o raЙ—aaЙ—o"
  17,40,"E hara Joomi mon suЙ“ani on Й“iЙ“Й“e worЙ“e, O jogitoo immorde e malaa'ikaЙ“e Й“en rewЙ“e? Pellet, onon hiЙ—in wowlude konngol mawnungol"
  17,41,"GomЙ—ii Men fensitii e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare fii yo Й“e waajitor, Й—um Й“eydaali Й“e si wonaa woЙ—Й—itagol"
  17,42,"Maaku : В« Si tawno no wonndi e makko, reweteeЙ—i wano Й“e wiвҖҷiri non awa Й—i Й—aЙ“Й“ayno laawol ummaade Jom Arsi o.\" @Corrected"
  17,43,"Senayee wonanii Mo, O Toowii gaayi e ko Й“e wi'ata Toowal Mawnungal"
  17,44,"No subunhinannde Mo kammuuli Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i e leydi ndin e Й“en wonuЙ“e e majji, alaa e hay e huunde si wanaa hinde Subunhinaade sabu Yettugol Mo, kono on faamataa subunhinaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, pellet, Kanko O wonii MunГұiiЙ—o Surroowo"
  17,45,Si a janngii Alqur'aanaare nden Men waЙ—ay hakkonde maa e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laahara on heedo suuЙ—iingo
  17,46,"Men waЙ—i e dow Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en cokooЙ—e fii wata Й“e faamu nde [Alqur'aanaare nden] e ka noppi maЙ“Й“e kadi teddeele, si a jantike Joomi maaЙ—a ka nder Alqur'aanaare Kanko Tun Й“e huccinay Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko Й“e dogooЙ“e"
  17,47,"Ko Menen Anndi ko Й“e heЙ—otoo kon, tuma Й“e heЙ—otoo faade e maaЙ—a [yo NulaaЙ—o], e tuma Й“e sowndondirta=ndeeydata, tuma nde tooГұooЙ“e Й“en wi'ata: В«On jokkaali si wanaa gorko mbilЙ—aaЙ—o=bilaadoВ»"
  17,48,"Ndaarii [yo NulaaЙ—o] ko honno Й“e piyiranay maa mise=yeruuji, Й“e majjii Й“e hattantaake [heЙ“ude] laawol"
  17,49,"ЖҒe wi'i: В«E hara si men wonii Жҙi'e e mbuЙ—u, haray ko men immintinoyteeЙ“e tagu hesu?В»"